text: Uhldingen-Mühlhofen is an German municipality at the northern shore of Lake Constance, between Überlingen and Meersburg. It is part of the district of Bodensee. It is home to the Pfahlbauten open-air museum in Unteruhldingen and the Birnau basilica. Uhldingen-Mühlhofen has three villages: Unteruhldingen, Oberuhldingen and Mühlhofen. == References == == Other websites == * Official website * Pfahlbauten open-air museum Category:Bodenseekreis
